  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>Foes are surprised by your skilled use of unorthodox and improvised weapons.</em> <br /><br /></p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites</strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<p class=\"stat-block-1\">You do not suffer any penalties for using an improvised weapon. Unarmed opponents are flatfooted against any attacks you make with an improvised weapon. You receive a +1 circumstance bonus on attack rolls made with thrown splash weapons.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Normal</strong></p>\n<p class=\"stat-block-1\">You take a &ndash;4 penalty on attack rolls made with an improvised weapon.</p>",
